Dr Adam Cobb was taken into custody on Friday in Portsmouth, New Hampshire . 
  He was arrested for receipt and distribution of child pornography . 
  Cobb was in the US working as a director at the prestigious US Naval War College in Rhode Island . 
  He worked for the federal government, the RAAF and Governor-General Sir Peter Cosgrove in East Timor . 
  He allegedly uploaded images of child porn to the social networking site, Tumblr . 
  If convicted he faces 20 years' jail . 
 